Outside interests
'Please take my child' - the Guardian, classified ads and 1930s Germany.¬†Link
Berkshire Hathaway‚Äôs stock price might break the stock market's computers.¬†Link
Things we discover due to cheap camera drones: sharks off Malibu beaches, and a surfer who touched a Great White Shark without noticing.¬†Link
Trassel - an interactive web toy.¬†Link
An AI communication coach.¬†Link


























